{"tid":1583272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日屯門上訴得直好鬼，大家小心","createTime":"2019-09-20T13:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T14:44:41.000Z","uid":300592,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d6a138039dd6758aded40f72cb027eff9119a711","tid":1583272,"uid":300592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:51:52.000Z","msg":"上次天水圍親子遊行都唔批不反對通知書，但偏偏聽日何妖吹雞就批畀我哋，會唔會伏咗啲？<br />\n唔係叫大家唔出，但真係要小心，因為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">何妖班人嘅最終目標唔係清連儂牆，而係撩交打／打人，然後令我哋畀黑警拉</span></strong>。<br />\n要諗定聽日入到屯公嘅話點走，如果何妖班人嚟埋，黑警會唔會封晒出口？咁我哋就畀人大圍捕？<br />\n總之聽日萬事小心，希望係我諗多咗。"},{"pid":"2927aabd2bd321cc8e23f7b0622b8663a2bca20a","tid":1583272,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:52:18.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊 - 會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人 - 食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG1y3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=76befbf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"4735cd8d51f6a82402ac84ef7b38e7a7ca56a1be","tid":1583272,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:52:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9fc30071957ed5e5754818b6981b045187fc968e","tid":1583272,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img